We are happy to announce that on the occasion of the @giambattistavalliparis x @hm collection launch, we are holding an open casting call to find the next Valli Star to walk the runway show in Rome, Italy, on October 24th.

Send your application including full name, age, height, contact information, a short motivation why you are the one we are looking for, along with 2 images (portrait and full body) and a video (full body walking) now to GBVxHM@giambattistavalli.com to join the Valli Family. 
All genders are welcome!

We look forward to hearing from you! 
#project🖤

Happy to reveal the campaign video for the @giambattistavalliparis x @hm . The collection will be out on November 7. Thank you to @metralas @macpiggott @kendalljenner @hermusicofficial @urnotchrislee @chiaraferragni @cameronmonoghan @claradeshayes @_this__is__luka @pg_dmcasting @themelanieward @thevalgarland @hollosmithhead for bringing this vision into light! #project🖤
Tune in today, September 30th at 1.30 PM CET, to enjoy the Giambattista Valli Spring/Summer ‘20 collection. LIVE on Instagram, GiambattistaValli.com and YouTube.com/fashion @youtube
